> First question: can I take off the steering wheel, re-align it horizontally
and re-seat it?

Not a good idea. Doing this will cause your turn signals not to cancel
correctly.  Yeah, I know: big deal, right? Probably why you get stuck behind a
car that has the left turn signal on for the past 5 miles.....
Center the wheel using the drag link.

